item.title: Proxy
item.description: Proxy package main import "fmt" type Greeter interface { Greet() } type DogGreeter struct { name string } func (g DogGreeter) Greet() { return g.name+": Bork Bork!" } func channel(g Greeter) { fmt.Println(g.Greet()) } func main() { dog := DogGreeter{"Sparkles"} channel(dog) }
